Hi

You could try to declare the ###### as a different trial

e.g. 

+1 * "response" ;
0 "#####";
+2 * "quite interesting" ;
0 "#######";

or a variant of this

then of course you have to be careful with the scrambling (if you want
to scramble, you have to block the the ### trials with the $ sign)

X.

